Description:
Period Charm and Modern Style
** THIS PROPERTY IS AVAILABLE FOR PRIVATE INSPECTIONS ONLY **
Offers close Monday 30 March @ 5pm (unless sold prior)
The charm of period features sits harmoniously alongside contemporary comforts within this warm & inviting home in a convenient & easily accessible locale.
Beyond a sun-drenched weatherboard facade & white picket fence, the high ceilings & timber floorboards through the spacious living & dining areas are the real highlights.
Two generous living spaces offer direct access to separate decked alfresco zones, opening the home to an indoor/outdoor lifestyle of ease & entertainment. A recently updated timber-topped kitchen provides a creative addition, with bespoke tiling, stainless steel appliances & matte black sink in the central island bench, perfect for casual dining for the entire family.
Custom floor-to-ceiling robes are on display in the large master bedroom benefiting from an ensuite bathroom & French doors to the backyard, while two further bedrooms boast built-in robes & share a neat spa-bathroom with dual access from the 2nd bedroom.
A concealed Euro laundry, walk-in pantry, split system A/C, evaporative cooling, ducted heating & ceiling fans add to the stylish interiors, while outside features 2 water tanks (2,300L), 10 2.5kw solar panels, a large double garage & additional off-street parking adjacent to the landscaped gardens & lush backyard.
Enjoy the ease of this spectacular period beauty, set within an easy 15-minute walk to Yarraman station & within moments to the town centre, Dandenong Market & excellent schools, with quick & easy Eastlink access within 800m.

Description:
Modern Delight in Top Location!

The comfortable lounge flows through to the spacious balcony & dining area & tiled hostess kitchen fitted with under bench oven, gas hot plates & dishwasher. The rear deck leads down to a private courtyard & access to the remote controlled garage. This unit is immaculate throughout & the heating & air conditioning is for your comfort. Don't miss this impressive property in the popular Metro Village estate, close to public transport & Eastlink. Great to live in or sit back & reap the benefits as an investor. INSPECTION WILL IMPRESS!

Situated just a 10-minute walk to the local train station and even closer to the high street shops, this is a property that features excellent walkability for easy, convenient living. Dandenong Primary School and Dandenong High School are moments away, the huge plaza and market are a three-minute drive from your door, and the highway is nearby for hassle-free commuting.
Located in a quiet complex, this spacious townhouse showcases a contemporary façade and attractive street appeal. Once inside, you'll be impressed by the open-plan family/meal zone with gleaming tiles and plenty of room for relaxing in front of the TV or dining with guests. The connecting kitchen is bright and clean with stylish benchtops, quality appliances, lots of cabinet space, and an adjoining laundry.
As you move to the upper level of the property, you'll notice the expansive landing area which is currently in use as a study but couldeasily be transformed into a peaceful retreat. The nearby master bedroom is of a generous size with abundant storage and a private en suite. The remaining two bedrooms have their own built-in robes and share the pleasant family bathroom which includes a lovelyvanity with stone benchtop, a large bathtub and separate WC.
Completing this superb residence is high ceilings, ducted heating, split system air conditioning to both levels, pendant lighting, and blinds and curtains throughout.
Providing easy upkeep is the exterior of this fantastic find with a patio area that's ideal for outdoor dining all year round. There's also a double garage and 3000 litre water tank.
Can you see yourself living here? Don't hesitate, enquire today!

First Time on Market!
Nestled in one of, if not, the best streets of Dandenong, this immaculate family home is ready to welcome their new owners! Immaculately looked after by the original owners over the decades, this gorgeous haven is perfect for a growing family. Featuring a master bedroom with BIR & en-suite; 2 extra generous bedrooms with built in robes, a study/family room that can easily be changed into a 4th bedroom, and a separate central bathroom and toilet to assist with the morning traffic.
With the concept of family in mind, a versatile floorplan provides convenience with multiple living areas; including big formal lounge room and dining areas, a meals area that connects onto the updated kitchen, with copious amount of storage, tiled splash back and plenty of bench space for meal preparations.
Externally, the gardens have been manicured and offers plenty of space for growing your own organic vegetables. With double garage and double carport, parking will never be an issue again.
With all amenities within a short commute, it really does offer the most convenient lifestyle. Bus stop is just around the corner, Dandening High School just 10 mins walk away, Dandenong Market and Plaza only a short drive and easy access to major road arterials, you simply can not look past this chance.
